data.description: Come to the quiet gated community of the Grove Village neighborhood of Henry County and fall in love with the recently built 5 bedroom, 3 bath corner lot beauty just waiting for you to move in! Nicely appointed with a brick hearth wood burning fireplace in the family room. The kitchen has granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and a tiled backsplash.  This wonderful home comes equipped with two HVACs, two Water Heaters, LVP flooring on the main level, and all electric utilities.  The brick-front home is intricately set with a sophisticated security system that comes with smart home controls and smart thermostat capabilities. You will love the large rooms throughout and the cozy, yet spacious upper level primary suite that has a huge walk- in closet, dual vanities with a garden tub and a separate shower in the suite bath. The amenities in the neighborhood include a basketball court and playground for your family and guests to enjoy! Just minutes away from the shoppes at Tanger Outlet, this wonderfully cared for beauty will not last long! **Seller offering $5,000 towards closing costs on a full price offer!
